Package: nima
Title: Nima Hejazi's R Toolbox
Version: 0.4.7
Authors@R: person("Nima", "Hejazi", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                  email = "nh@nimahejazi.org",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7127-2789"))
Description: A personal R toolbox containing aids for statistical research and
  scientific computing. These include, for example, utilities that supplement
  the existing idiosyncrasies of R, extend existing plotting functionality and
  aesthetics, provide alternative presentations of matrix decompositions, and
  enhance access to systems-level information.
Depends:
  R (>= 3.2.3)
